---
/**
 * Archived Post Warning Component
 * 
 * Displays a warning banner for archived posts that are kept for historical purposes.
 * Matches the Jekyll archived post warning functionality.
 */
---

<div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
  <strong>‚ùó Heads up!</strong> This post is archived and here for historical purposes. It may no longer be accurate or reflect my views. Proceed at your own risk.
</div>

<style>
  .alert {
    position: relative;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
  }

  .alert-warning {
    color: var(--bs-warning-text-emphasis, #664d03);
    background-color: var(--bs-warning-bg-subtle, #fff3cd);
    border-color: var(--bs-warning-border-subtle, #ffecb5);
  }
</style>
